The '''Dack Track''' was a [[blob racing]] track that was given to [[Slish Fondine]] by [[Mistal]], the [[Duchess/Legends|Duchess]] of [[Dargul]] in [[11 ABY/Legends|11 ABY]] as a reward for returning her missing consort, [[Dack]]. Dack had been apprehended by Fondine for cheating, since he had entered an illegally-enhanced [[blob]] into a number of races in order to earn enough [[Galactic Credit Standard/Legends|credits]] to buy passage offplanet in order to get away from the Duchess. Fondine had originally intended to execute him, but [[Lando Calrissian/Legends|Lando Calrissian]] convinced him to return the fleeing Dack in order to avoid an intersystem incident. The track was, ironically, named for him.

